data.title: We Dive at Dawn (1943)
data.meta_description: World War II drama about a mission to hunt and destroy a dangerous German battleship in the Baltic which goes wrong when the British submarine runs short on fuel. A crew member with a flair for the German language is forced to disembark on an enemy-occupied Danish island.
